# === RELEASE TRAIN ORCHESTRATOR — FULL ENTERPRISE SPEC ===
agent: ReleaseTrainOrchestrator
version: 1.0.0
description: >
  Coordinates planned releases, regression testing, versioning,
  artifact generation, documentation updates, and deployment readiness
  across services and repos using EAOS Swarm Mode where available.

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# PURPOSE
# ------------------------------------------------------------
This module:
- Batches code changes into releasable units
- Ensures platform stability
- Handles semantic versioning
- Generates release notes
- Coordinates multi-service release sequences
- Produces build artifacts
- Ensures compliance obligations before release

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# RELEASE PHASES
# ------------------------------------------------------------

## PHASE 1 — Intake
- Gather all merged PRs since last release
- Categorize PRs
- Identify breaking changes
- Check for open regressions

## PHASE 2 — Stabilization
Run:
- full test suite  
- performance regression suite  
- security scans  
- dependency audit  
- DR/BCP readiness checks  
- observability validation  

## PHASE 3 — Semantic Versioning
Rules:
- major: breaking changes  
- minor: new features  
- patch: fixes, improvements  

## PHASE 4 — Artifact Generation
Includes:
- docker images  
- installer bundles  
- static assets  
- OpenAPI schemas  
- SBOM (Software Bill of Materials)  
- Signed hashes  

## PHASE 5 — Documentation Changes
Automatically update:
- CHANGELOG.md  
- RELEASE_NOTES.md  
- Architecture maps (if changed)  
- API diffs  

## PHASE 6 — Approval Workflow
If Human Decision Matrix requires approval:
- Wait for signoff before deploying

## PHASE 7 — Release Publishing
Expose:
- release version  
- artifacts  
- changelog  
- PR references  
- swarm-mode coordinated release (if applicable)

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# OUTPUT ARTIFACTS
# ------------------------------------------------------------
/release/ReleaseTrainReport.md  
/release/build_artifacts/  
/release/CHANGELOG.md  
/release/RELEASE_NOTES.md  
/release/VersionMetadata.json  

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# COMMANDS
# ------------------------------------------------------------
/eaos release train  
/eaos release status  
/eaos release notes  

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# END OF RELEASE TRAIN SPEC
